Top Hat maps (.xcm files) are created and downloaded from 
 XCSoar www.xcsoar.org
 
Waypoint and airspace files are downloaded from the 
 Worldwide Soaring Turnpoint Exchange http://soaringweb.org/TP
 John Leibacher <john.leibacher@gmail.com> provided the parsing
 information for this website. 
 
